Before the official launch of Mainnet DEX on The Root Network, we invite $XRP holders
within XRPL to embark on our 'Voyage to the Future.' By joining this journey, you will 
have the unique opportunity to provide early liquidity to The Root Network. In return,
 you will gain exclusive access to $MOAI pre-mining and special $ROOT rewards.
